            "title": "A multi-scale approach to facultative paedomorphosis of European newts (Salamandridae) in the Montenegrin karst: Distribution pattern, environmental variables, and conservation",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Mathieu",
